				{
					"Description": "With this function you can asynchronously add an image as a sprite, loading it from an external source where the image file to be loaded should always be in either *.png, *.gif, *.jpg/jpeg or *.json format (*json files are used for loading skeleton animation sprites made with Spine). This function will generate an Image Loaded asynchronous event when the sprite has been loaded.",
					"Parameter": [
