				{
					"Description": "This function takes two previously created (or included) sprite indexes, and copies the image from one to the other. In this way you can copy (or \"clone\") one sprite into another index. Note that you cannot copy to a game asset. You have to have created the sprite to be copied to previously using the sprite_add() or sprite_duplicate() functions.",
