					"_ReturnType": "Undefined",
					"_Pure": "false"
				},
				{
					"Description": "With this function you can set the properties of the collision mask that a sprite should have. If you select either automatic (0) or full image (1) as the bounding box mode then the individual bounding box values can be set to 0. However, for a user-defined mask (2) you will have to set these values.",
