					"_Pure": "true"
				},
				{
					"Description": "With this function you can add a new (empty) time line into your game. You should make sure to use the function timeline_delete() whenever you no longer wish it to prevent any possible memory leaks. To add moments to a timeline created in this way, see the function timeline_moment_add_script().",
