				{
					"Description": "This function will send a request to the server for information on all current challenges and will trigger a callback Social Asynchronous Event which contains the async_load map populated with the relevant key/value pairs. The id key of this DS Map is used to identify the correct callback (there can be more than one trigger function for any given asynchronous event), and will be paired with the constant achievement_challenge_list_received as well as a number of other key/value pairs for each challenge.",
