					"Description": "With this function you can save a screenshot of a part of the game as it currently appears in the game display. The selection coordinates are based on the absolute size of the display (or window if not fullscreen), so (0, 0) is always the top-left hand corner of the screen (or window).",
					"Parameter": [
						{
							"_Name": "fname",
							"_Type": "String",
							"_Optional": "false",
							"__text": "The filename for the screenshot to save"
						},
						{
							"_Name": "x",
