				{
					"Description": "With this function you can draw either an outline of a rectangle or a filled rectangle where the (x1, y1) position is the top left corner and the (x2, y2) position is the bottom right corner. Please note that the rectangle being drawn may need different values (+/-1 on the x, y, or width or height) to be drawn with the desired dimensions due to differences across the various supported platforms.",
