				{
					"Description": "With this function you can draw part of any surface at a given position within the room. As with draw_surface() you can specify a surface, but you then need to specify the relative coordinates within the surface of an area to select for drawing. This means that a left position of 0 and a top position of 0 would be the top left corner of the surface and all further coordinates should be taken from that position.",
