					"Description": "With this function you can check a position for a collision with another instance or all instances of an object.\n\t\t\t\n\t\t\tWhen you use this you are checking a single point in the room for an instance or an object.\n\t\t\t\n\t\t\tThe check will be done against the bounding box of the instance or against the mask of the instance if that instance has precise collisions checked.",
