				{
					"Description": "With this function you can send a request to connect to a server. The function takes the socket id to connect through and requires you to give the IP address to connect to as well as the port to connect through, and if the connection fails a value of less than 0 will be returned.\n\t\t\t\n\t\t\tThis connection uses a special protocol that ensures only GameMaker games connect to each other, however if you need to connect to a server that is not a GameMaker game, you can use network_connect_raw().",
