					"_Pure": "true"
				},
				{
					"Description": "With this function you can take two colors and then merge them together to make a new color. The amount of each of the component colors can be defined by changing the \"amount\" argument, where a value of 0 will return the first color (col1), a value of 1 will return the second color (col2) and a value in between will return the corresponding mix. For example, a value of 0.5 will mix the two colors equally.",
					"Parameter": [
