					"_Locale": "US",
					"_Pure": "false"
				},
				{
					"Description": "With this function you can set a hue, saturation and value range for all particles of the given type. In this way you can create particles of the same hue but different saturations, or of different hues but the same value (luminosity), etc. All values must be between 0 and 255.",
