					"_Name": "rollback_game_full",
					"_Type": "Real",
					"_Deprecated": "false",
					"_FeatureFlag": "rollback",
					"__text": "Fired when the game you're trying to join is already full"
				},
				{
					"_Name": "rollback_game_info",
					"_Type": "Real",
					"_Deprecated": "false",
					"_FeatureFlag": "rollback",
					"__text": "Fired when you receive back info about the game (in rollback_event_param) player_id and num_players"
				},
				{
					"_Name": "rollback_connection_rejected",
					"_Type": "Real",
					"_Deprecated": "false",
					"_FeatureFlag": "rollback",
					"__text": "Fired when connection attempt was rejected. The error can be caused by invalid token, mismatch in client versions, mismatch in protocol versions. Multiplayer session is closed automatically before event is fired."
				},
				{
					"_Name": "rollback_protocol_rejected",
					"_Type": "Real",
					"_Deprecated": "false",
					"_FeatureFlag": "rollback",
					"__text": "Fired when connection attempt was rejected. The error means that client uses obsolete version of the protocol. Before this event is fired GM will show an error message in the UI. Multiplayer session is closed automatically before event is fired."
				},
				{
					"_Name": "rollback_end_game",
					"_Type": "Real",
					"_Deprecated": "false",
					"_FeatureFlag": "rollback",
					"__text": "Fired when server wants clients to stop the game. Usually this event means that clients are in inconsistent state. Multiplayer session is closed automatically before event is fired"
				},
				{
					"_Name": "rollback_chat_message",
					"_Type": "Real",
					"_Deprecated": "false",
					"_FeatureFlag": "rollback",
					"__text": "Fired when you receive a chat message, including those sent by the local player (in rollback_event_param) message, from and to"
				},
				{
					"_Name": "rollback_player_prefs",
					"_Type": "Real",
					"_Deprecated": "false",
					"_FeatureFlag": "rollback",
					"__text": "Fired when you receive new preferences set by any of the players in the game, including those set by the local player (in rollback_event_param) preferences, and player_id"
				},
				{
					"_Name": "rollback_high_latency",
					"_Type": "Real",
					"_Deprecated": "false",
					"_FeatureFlag": "rollback",
					"__text": "Fired when the latency to the server is too high and it's impossible to run the game. Multiplayer session is closed automatically before event is fired"
				},
				{
					"_Name": "rollback_connect_info",
					"_Type": "Real",
					"_Deprecated": "false",
					"_FeatureFlag": "rollback",
					"__text": "Fired when you get info of where players should connect (in rollback_event_param) share_url"
				},
				{
					"_Name": "rollback_connect_error",
					"_Type": "Real",
					"_Deprecated": "false",
					"_FeatureFlag": "rollback",
					"__text": "Fired when you fail to connect to the backend"
